{"tid":1563242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵出入閘問題","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:34:26.000Z","uid":298237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f00c33143215ab13d7d1acf746f9a83494ceb992","tid":1563242,"uid":298237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"大家好,小弟係一位身體唔好又有些少潔闢既打工仔<br />\n我好容易接觸到一D細菌就會病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於工作關係 返工放工要搭港鐵 <br />\n平時小弟專容/出閘入閘既方式好特別 成日嚇親人地<br />\n首先我係帶住口罩手套  拍卡&gt;出/入閘&gt;拉埋個滾筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個閘既滾筒一日入面俾幾萬或幾十萬人用過 實係好dirty  我好驚要接觸到佢所以要跳過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近日我經常聽到話有人好得閒捉人跳閘(好彩我搭個兩個站冇人咁做) 我個人非常好驚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有一日我要去深水埗/黃大仙出閘我好驚俾人捉住架<br />\n<br />\n第一.我一定要搭港鐵 冇得搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二.我出入閘個個位冇三角閘 所以先咁做<br />\n第三.我有諗過搵職員開個欄俾我出入 但係好麻煩人地 人地會當我低能架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下有冇朋友有同我一樣既問題發生而你地又點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae648ead64415a26f7fabcca97294259dceacabc","tid":1563242,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:34:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}